parently is not applied retroactively to accounts created long time ago.}}\n| {{unknown}}\n| {{no|Yes}}\n|-\n! style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Zoho Office Suite|Zoho Mail]]\n| {{no|Yes}}\n| {{no|Yes}}\n| {{no|Yes}}\n|-\n|}\n\n===Secure delivery===\nFeatures to reduce the risk of third-party tracking and interception of the email content; measures to increase the [[Email deliverability|deliverability]] of correct outbound messages.\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"font-size: 85%; text-align:center; width:auto;\"\n!\n! colspan=\"3\" | Anti-[[Wiretapping|interception]]\n! colspan=\"4\" | Outbound anti-[[Email spoofing|spoofing]] and deliverability\n! rowspan=\"2\" | Other{{efn|Additional notes like usage of [[DMARC]], [[ARC]]}}\n|-\n! Product\n! STARTTLS (outbound){{efn|Ability to use STARTTLS over SMTP}}\n! STARTTLS (inbound){{efn|Verified with https://starttls-everywhere.org/ or other}}\n! Tracking content prevention<ref name=EFF2019>{{cite web|url=https://www.eff.org/deeplinks/2019/01/stop-tracking-my-emails|title=(Don't) Return to Sender: How to Protect Yourself From Email Tracking|authors=Sydney Li and Bennett Cyphers|date=2019-01-09}}</ref>\n! Basic SPF{{efn|SPF is configured and outbound mail passes SPF test from default webmail and SMTP}}\n! SPF for custom domain and client{{efn|SPF can be configured on a custom domain with reserved IP address or shared addresses and anti-spoofing measures}}\n!Default DKIM{{efn|Outbound mail has a default DKIM signature by default}}\n!DKIM for custom domain and client{{efn|A custom DKIM signature can be generated for outbound mail and configured on a custom server}}\n|-\n! style=\"text-align:left;\" |Alice.it, [[Tin.it]]\n| ?\n| {{No}}<ref name=gtremailred/>\n|-\n! style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[AOL Mail]]\n| {{No}}<ref name=gtremailred>{{cite web|url=https://transparencyreport.google.com/safer-email/overview?encrypt_region_table=encryption_level:RED;region:001&lu=encrypt_region_table|title=Google transparency report fo