e, Yandex PDD supports up to 1000 mailboxes without verification of legal use)\n| [[HTML]]/ [[JavaScript]]/ [[CSS]]/[[Ajax (programming)|Ajax]]\n| {{yes}}<br>([[Dr.Web]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://help.yandex.ru/mail/|title=\u0427\u0430\u0441\u0442\u044b\u0435 \u0432\u043e\u043f\u0440\u043e\u0441\u044b \u0432 \u042f\u043d\u0434\u0435\u043a\u0441.\u041f\u043e\u0447\u0442\u0435 \u2014 \u041f\u043e\u0447\u0442\u0430 (\u0441\u0442\u0430\u0440\u044b\u0439 \u0438\u043d\u0442\u0435\u0440\u0444\u0435\u0439\u0441) \u2014 \u042f\u043d\u0434\u0435\u043a\u0441.\u041f\u043e\u043c\u043e\u0449\u044c|publisher=|accessdate=January 26, 2017}}</ref>)\n| Configurable or/and if discarded by antivirus\n| {{Yes}}, only from confirmed addresses<ref>{{cite web|url=http://help.yandex.com/mail/?id=1114258|title=Sender information \u2014 Mail \u2014 Yandex.Support|publisher=|accessdate=January 26, 2017}}</ref>\n| {{Yes|Plus addressing}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://help.yandex.ru/mail/reg.xml|title=\u0420\u0435\u0433\u0438\u0441\u0442\u0440\u0430\u0446\u0438\u044f \u2014 \u041f\u043e\u0447\u0442\u0430 (\u0441\u0442\u0430\u0440\u044b\u0439 \u0438\u043d\u0442\u0435\u0440\u0444\u0435\u0439\u0441) \u2014 \u042f\u043d\u0434\u0435\u043a\u0441.\u041f\u043e\u043c\u043e\u0449\u044c|publisher=|accessdate=January 26, 2017}}</ref>\n| {{No}}\n| {{No}}\n|-\n! [[Zoho Office Suite|Zoho Mail]]\n| {{partial|Yes if you use Zoho domain, if you use your own domain then Premium plans only}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.zoho.com/mail/help/adminconsole/subscription.html#alink0|title=Features exclusive to Paid Plans|publisher=|accessdate=June 1, 2018}}</ref>\n| {{partial|Premium plans only (POP, IMAP, SMTP)}}\n| {{Yes|Yes (POP)}}\n| {{Yes|[[Extensible Messaging and Presence Protocol|XMPP]], [[Google Talk]], [[AOL Instant Messenger]], [[ICQ]], [[Yahoo! Messenger]]}}\n| {{Partial|Business plans only, including free plan}}\n| [[Ajax (programming)|Ajax]]\n| {{Yes}}\n| ?\n| {{Yes}}\n| ?\n| {{No}}\n| {{No}}\n|- class=\"sortbo