o-response), mobile app for smartphones, integration with Digiposte (a virtual safe-deposit box that allows you to safely archive all your documents in a secured place, including legal documents).\n|-\n! style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Mailfence]]\n| Client-side encryption with email expiration, Digital signatures, Full OpenPGP inter-operability and support, Integrated account keystore, Multiple PGP keypair support, Public keyserver connection, Full reversibility and key revocation<ref>{{cite web|url=https://blog.mailfence.com/mailfence-unique-secure-and-private-email/ |title=Why mailfence is a unique, secure and private email service}}</ref>, Full email-suite, Shared mailbox and collaboration with group members\n|-\n! style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Outlook.com]]\n| [[One-time password]], Mobile alerts, Account verification via SMS or voice call in some countries, Rules,<ref name=\"windows.microsoft.com\">[http://windows.microsoft.com/en-gb/windows/outlook/clean-inbox Clean, clutter-free inbox] Outlook.com</ref> Messages grouped into \"conversations\", Scheduled Cleanup,<ref name=\"windows.microsoft.com\"/> Filter to e.g. only see newsletters or Emails from contacts,<ref name=\"windows.microsoft.com\"/> Recover deleted emails;<ref>[http://windows.microsoft.com/en-gb/windows/outlook/recover-deleted-messages Recover deleted messages] Outlook.com</ref> Key encryption for paid accounts<ref>{{cite web|url=https://support.office.com/en-us/article/learn-about-encrypted-messages-in-outlook-com-3521aa01-77e3-4cfd-8a13-299eb60b1957|title=Learn about encrypted messages in Outlook.com|website=support.office.com|accessdate=December 10, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n! style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[ProtonMail]]\n| Client-side encryption, email expiration, automatic encryption for ProtonMail-ProtonMail emails, optional email encryption for messages from ProtonMail to other providers\n|-\n! style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Rackspace]]\n|White label option for resellers; Webmail chat; Recover deleted emails; Shared contacts and calendars; SMS based password recovery; Integrated Cloud Drive file storage with document and spreadsheet editors; Attach files from Dropbox<ref name=\":0\" />\n|-\n! style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Rediffmail]]\n| sign-in via [[Google]], [[Yahoo!]], [[Facebook]], [[Twitter]], Mobile Sync; Indrive.\n|-\n! style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Tutanota]]\n| Client-side encryption, automatic encryption of mailbox, automatic encryption of emails between Tutanota users, optional email encryption for messages from Tutanota to other providers\n|-\n! style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Yandex Mail]]\n| No ads, email for own domains (Yandex PDD), scheduled email delivery, SMS verification, sign-in via Twitter, VK, Facebook, Google Profile\n|-\n! style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Zoho Office Suite|Zoho Mail]]\n| Email Sharing, Folder Sharing, Collaborating with other users by Chat/ Social media for organization, Filters, Schedule and send emails, reminders, Notes, Tasks, Bookmarks and so on.\n|}\n\n==Features==\n<!-- Please do not add new entries to this table unless there is a Wikipedia article about the product. Thank you. -->\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"font-size: 85%; text-align:center; width:auto;\"\n|-p\n! Service name\n! Automatic forwarding\n! Email client access{{efn|name=POP3Support|Most mail services that do not support POP3 access can be accessed through the [[FreePOPs]] mail proxy software.}}\n! Client email for other server\n! Integration with IM service\n! Domain<br>Name<br>customization\n! Interface<br>script<br>technique\n! Virus scanning\n! Filters out emails with executable attachments\n! Custom \"From:\" Address\n! Address modifiers ([[Plus address|subaddressing]])\n! Server hosted public keyring (for encryption)\n! Shared key encryption\n|-\n! [[AOL Mail]]\n| {{No}}\n| {{Yes}}<br>([[POP3]], [[IMAP]], [[SMTP]])\n| {{Yes}}{{efn|Through AOL Easy Transfer}}\n| style=\"background:#dfd;\"| [[AOL Instant Messenger]]\n| {{No}}{{efn|T